data.description: Presenting an exquisite two-story residence nestled in the charming neighborhood of Lancaster, complete with the eco-friendly advantage of solar panels and a convenient attached two-car garage. This splendid abode boasts a well-lit and inviting floorplan, encompassing three bedrooms, three bathrooms, and a generous 1,913 square feet of living area. Elegance abounds in every corner, with laminate and tile flooring gracing the interior, complemented by tasteful lighting fixtures. Abundant storage solutions are seamlessly integrated, including a dedicated laundry area for your convenience. The home offers both a spacious living room and a cozy family room adorned with a charming fireplace. Indulge your culinary aspirations in the well-appointed kitchen, replete with a central island, sleek countertops, stainless steel appliances, and pristine white cabinetry. The bedrooms are havens of comfort and light, each adorned with a ceiling fan/light fixture and ample closet space. The primary bedroom stands out with its luxurious walk-in closet and an en-suite bathroom featuring dual sink vanities for added privacy. Beyond the interiors, the exterior presents an expansive yard, offering plenty of room for outdoor activities and relaxation on the patio, all enveloped in a setting of tranquility and seclusion. The canvas is open for your creative ideas to personalize and transform this space into your dream oasis. Conveniently situated, this home enjoys a prime location in proximity to Stater Bros Market, Walgreens, an array of popular dining establishments, schools, and more. Embrace the opportunity to shape this residence into your own haven in an enviable locale.
